title: Yosemite Dawn Wall Climbers Reach The Top After 19 Days
teaser: Climbers Tommy Caldwell and Kevin Jorgeson finished their historic first free climb on El Capitan's Dawn Wall in Yosemite National Park. Melissa Block talks with the duo about their 19-day effort.
